Final Project in Python Programming
Program returns weather forecast for Rochester NY from the National Weather Service
API.
The following files are included with this package:
config.py
forecast.py
main.py
nwsclient.py
visual.py

To install:
Simply unzip the package in the directory of your choice. Keep all the files in the same directory

To run:
must have Python3 installed prior to operating.
from the command line, type: python3 main.py

